alias ArcFurnace0 d0
alias ArcFurnace1 d1
alias ArcFurnace2 d2
alias ArcFurnace3 d3
alias ArcFurnace4 d4
alias ArcFurnace5 d5

alias ArcFurnaceRefID r0
alias InputItemQuantity r1
alias ArcFurnaceStatus r2

Start:
sleep 2
l ArcFurnaceRefID ArcFurnace0 ReferenceId
jal CheckItemInput

bdns ArcFurnace1 Start
l ArcFurnaceRefID ArcFurnace1 ReferenceId
jal CheckItemInput

bdns ArcFurnace2 Start
l ArcFurnaceRefID ArcFurnace2 ReferenceId
jal CheckItemInput

bdns ArcFurnace3 Start
l ArcFurnaceRefID ArcFurnace3 ReferenceId
jal CheckItemInput

bdns ArcFurnace4 Start
l ArcFurnaceRefID ArcFurnace4 ReferenceId
jal CheckItemInput

bdns ArcFurnace5 Start
l ArcFurnaceRefID ArcFurnace5 ReferenceId
jal CheckItemInput

j Start

CheckItemInput:
ls InputItemQuantity ArcFurnaceRefID 0 Quantity
bgtz InputItemQuantity TurnOnArcFurnace
s ArcFurnaceRefID On 0
j ra

TurnOnArcFurnace:
s ArcFurnaceRefID On 1
l ArcFurnaceStatus ArcFurnaceRefID Activate
beq ArcFurnaceStatus 1 ra
s ArcFurnaceRefID Activate 1
j ra
